                            85
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-2">
                    <span class="text-sm text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 flex items-center">
                        <svg class="w-3 h-3 mr-1"
                             fill="currentColor"
                             viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd"
